        CALM_DOWN_AYAME_HE_S_SHE_S_AN                                         = 7534,  -- Calm down, Ayame. He's/She's] an adventurer. It's his/her] job to go adventuring.
        WE_RE_HERE_TO_INVESTIGATE_SOMETHING_IT_COULD                          = 7535,  -- We're here to investigate something. It could get pretty dangerous, so I suggest taking a few steps back if you know what's good for you.
        WHY_CID_WHAT_BUSINESS_DO_YOU_HAVE_HERE                                = 7536,  -- Why, Cid. What business do you have here today?
        WELL_IF_IT_ISN_T_LITTLE_WOLFGANG_HOW                                  = 7537,  -- Well, if it isn't little Wolfgang. How have you been?
        WE_RE_HERE_TO_CHECK_OUT_THE_CRYSTAL                                   = 7538,  -- We're here to check out the Crystal Line. Recently I've been receiving some very strange readings from this area.
        ACCORDING_TO_THE_DATA_RETRIEVED_BY_A_REPUBLICAN                       = 7539,  -- According to the data retrieved by a Republican party that visited here last month, the once stable energy flow has begun to fluctuate.
        I_VE_NEVER_SEEN_SUCH_HIGH_READINGS                                    = 7540,  -- I've never seen such high readings...
        THE_FLOW_OF_ENERGY_IS_SO_OVERWHELMING_THAT                            = 7541,  -- The flow of energy is so overwhelming that the Telepoint you see over there was shattered to pieces! And now there are reports that a giant beast appeared over the sea, just to the north of Delkfutt's Tower.
        I_HAVE_A_BAD_FEELING_THAT_THESE_TWO                                   = 7542,  -- I have a bad feeling that these two events are connected, and that they're warning us of something worse to come.
        I_UNDERSTAND_THAT_RESEARCH_INCLINES_YOU_TO_PURSUE                     = 7543,  -- ... I understand that research inclines you to pursue these matters. However, I ask that you leave the investigation to the Duchy.
        EH_SO_THE_DUCHY_KNOWS_THE_CAUSE_OF                                    = 7544,  -- Eh? So the Duchy knows the cause of all these strange phenomena?
        NOT_EXACTLY_WE_HAVE_NUMEROUS_PARTIES_INVESTIGATING_THE                = 7545,  -- Not exactly. We have numerous parties investigating the situation. However, many of those sent into the field have...vanished.
        WE_CANNOT_ALLOW_ANY_MORE_ACCIDENTS_THE_DAMAGE                         = 7546,  -- We cannot allow any more accidents. The damage to Vana'diel would be great if we were to lose such an important engineer as you, Cid.
        HAH_LET_ME_GUESS_THE_SCIENTISTS_BACK_IN                               = 7547,  -- Hah! Let me guess... The scientists back in Jeuno told you to get rid of all those who got in their way.
        WHO_DO_THEY_THINK_THEY_ARE_COME_TO                                    = 7548,  -- Who do they think they are!? Come to think of it, I have good reason to believe that it's those lunatics that are causing all this trouble!
        WH_WHAT_IS_GOING_ON                                                   = 7549,  -- Wh-what is going on!?
        THERE_IS_NOTHING_OUT_OF_THE_ORDINARY_HERE_2                           = 7550,  -- There is nothing out of the ordinary here.
        YOU_CAN_HEAR_A_STRANGE_VOICE_ITEMS_ITEMS                              = 7551,  -- You can hear a strange voice... Items, items, la la la la la`t
        OH_MY_GOB_YOU_RE_ONE_OF_THOSE                                         = 7552,  -- Oh my Gob! You're one of those adventurerurers, aren't ya? You got nothin' on me, man./lady.] I was just mindin' my own businesesess, lookin' for junk an' stuff.
        HEY_WATCH_OUT_YOU_DON_T_WANNA_FIGHT                                   = 7553,  -- Hey, watch out. You don't wanna fight me. I'll turn you into meat jerky! Wait, how about you and me be friends instead? Sound good?
