        HI_THERE_I_M_YOUR_FRIENDLY_NEIGHBORHOOD_SMILE                         = 10958,  -- Hi there! I'm your friendly neighborhood smile sergeant! I'm in charge of running the [beginner/intermediate/advanced] level Smilebringer Boot Camp in this area.
        I_D_BE_THRILLED_TO_ANSWER_ANY_QUESTIONS                               = 10959,  -- I'd be thrilled to answer any questions you might have...and of course, sign you up, too! You'd like that, wouldn't you? Hmmm?
        WHAT_WILL_YOU_DO_UNDERTAKE_TRAINING_HEAR_AN                           = 10960,  -- What will you do? Undertake training. Hear an explanation. What's the qualifying time? What's the fastest time? Nothing.
        FANTASTIC_BUT_OH_IT_SEEMS_YOU_DON_T                                   = 10961,  -- Fantastic! But, oh...it seems you don't have %. Well, that's just too bad!
        IT_D_BE_MY_PLEASURE_HERE_GOES_NOTHING                                 = 10962,  -- It'd be my pleasure! Here goes nothing! Ahem! The Smilebringer Boot Camp was established for two purposes, the first being the ongoing training and conditioning of smilebringers. The second--and this is where you come in, yay!--is for us to scout hopefuls from the adventurer community to join our jovial ranks!
        THE_POPULATION_OF_VICIOUS_MONSTERS_HAS_GROWN_IN                       = 10963,  -- The population of vicious monsters has grown in recent years, you see. And because of this, more smilebringers were being--<gasp!>--injured in the line of duty than ever before.
        BUT_WE_WEREN_T_GOING_TO_TAKE_THAT                                     = 10964,  -- But we weren't going to take that sitting down, no siree. The day we smilebringers stop doing our job--that is, bringing smiles--is the day the world ends!
        WHATEVER_THE_PREDICAMENT_AND_NO_MATTER_THE_SIZE                       = 10965,  -- Whatever the predicament, and no matter the size of the ruszor-inflicted gash wound, we will--we must--pull through...for the sake of the children!
        WITH_THESE_HEART_WARMING_IDEALS_IN_MIND_THE                           = 10966,  -- With these heart-warming ideals in mind, the Smilebringer Boot Camp was established. Ta-da! Smilebringers graduating from this camp are better equipped to meet the ever-changing needs of these unstable times we live in.
        THE_RULES_ARE_AS_SIMPLE_AS_SUNSHINE_SMILEBRINGER                      = 10967,  -- The rules are as simple as sunshine. Smilebringer's honor! When I give you the word, run to each of the checkpoints we've set up in the area. Smile helpers are posted at each, so you can't miss them!
        TALK_TO_THE_SMILE_HELPERS_AND_THEY_LL                                 = 10968,  -- Talk to the smile helpers and they'll confirm your passage. The route you take is completely up to you--just be sure you don't miss any checkpoints. You got all that? Hmmm?
        I_LL_MARK_EACH_SMILE_HELPER_S_LOCATION                                = 10969,  -- I'll mark each smile helper's location on your map beforehand, so you don't need to worry about getting lost.
        ONCE_YOU_VE_FINISHED_VISITING_ALL_THE_CHECKPOINTS                     = 10970,  -- Once you've finished visiting all the checkpoints, you have to--you guessed it!--come back and report to me. It's okay, I won't bite!
        WHAT_I_WILL_DO_THOUGH_IS_TELL_YOU                                     = 10971,  -- What I will do, though, is tell you how quickly you completed the course. After all, to a smilebringer, speed is everything. Some folks run faster with a fell beast hot on their tail, but we smilebringers need no more than the thought of a child's laughter to spur us on! Zoom zoom!
        OH_AND_I_SHOULD_MENTION_THAT_AT_THIS                                  = 10972,  -- Oh, and I should mention that at this time of year, we're collecting donations in the form of a small fee to participate in the training. All proceeds go towards presents for the children during the Starlight Celebration. Thank you for your cooperation!
        ONE_MORE_THING_YOU_SHOULD_KNOW_IF_YOU                                 = 10973,  -- One more thing you should know. If you venture out of the area, the training will automatically be canceled. But I can trust you not to walk out on your favorite smile sergeant, right? Hmmm?
        SO_FAR_THE_FASTEST_TIME_IN_THIS_AREA                                  = 10974,  -- So far, the fastest time in this area is # minute[/s] # second[/s]. Wow! And the name of the greased lightning who set this record is %. Don't be forgetting that, you hear?
        WE_D_LIKE_ALL_PARTICIPANTS_TO_COMPLETE_THIS                           = 10975,  -- We'd like all participants to complete this area's course within # minute[/s] # second[/s]. A piece of cake for a strapping young wolf/vixen] like you, surely! And if you manage a time quicker than # minute[/s] # second[/s]...then you and I had better trade places! Oh, that would be so much fun, wouldn't it?
        AWWW_YOU_VE_MADE_THIS_SMILE_SERGEANT_VERY                             = 10976,  -- Awww... You've made this smile sergeant very sad... But I'll be glued to this spot, because I just know you'll be back to turn my frown upside down! Yes siree!
        AT_THIS_TIME_OF_YEAR_WE_RE_COLLECTING                                 = 10977,  -- At this time of year, we're collecting a donation of # gil from each participant. All proceeds go towards presents for the children. Oh, won't you think of the children? <Sniffle>...
        GIVE_TO_THE_CHILDREN_I_LIVE_TO_GIVE                                   = 10978,  -- Give to the children? I live to give! Charity begins at home.
        BUT_OF_COURSE_FIRST_I_LL_NEED_YOU                                     = 10979,  -- But of course! First, I'll need you to lend me your %... Oh, don't pout! I'll give it back as soon as I'm done, promise!
        YOU_LL_FIND_EACH_OF_THE_TEN_SMILE                                     = 10980,  -- You'll find each of the ten smile helpers by the points I've indicated. Don't forget to talk with every one of them or it won't count, okay?
        THERE_I_VE_MARKED_EACH_SMILE_HELPER_S                                 = 10981,  -- There! I've marked each smile helper's location for you. If you ever lose your bearings in the middle of a run, just open up your map and everything will be aaall right. Trust me! <Wink>
        SO_ARE_YOU_READY_STEADY_LEVEL_TRAINING_GO                             = 10982,  -- So, are you ready-steady? [Beginner/Intermediate/Advanced] level training...GO! Come on, pump those legs like there's no tomorrow!
        SINCE_THE_STARLIGHT_CELEBRATION_HAS_ENDED_WE_VE                       = 10983,  -- Since the Starlight Celebration has ended, we've had to make a few changes.
        BUT_THE_SMILEBRINGER_BOOT_CAMP_WILL_BE_AVAILABLE                      = 10984,  -- But the Smilebringer Boot Camp will be available for off-season conditioning the whole year round, so come back whenever you're in the mood. I'll be waiting for you!
        OH_YOU_RE_BACK_I_WAS_AFRAID_WE                                        = 10985,  -- Oh, you're back! I was afraid we'd lost you to some foul creature prowling the wilderness. Let's start from the top, shall we?
        OH_WHAT_RE_YOU_DOING_HERE_AREN_T                                      = 10986,  -- Oh, what're you doing here? Aren't you in the middle of a run right now? Couldn't stand to be parted from your favorite smile sergeant, maybe? Teehee!
        WHAT_WILL_YOU_DO_HEAR_AN_EXPLANATION_WHERE                            = 10987,  -- What will you do? Hear an explanation. Where're the smile helpers again? Cancel the training. Nothing.
        AWWW_THESE_RIVULETS_OF_TEARS_STREAMING_DOWN_MY                        = 10988,  -- Awww... These rivulets of tears streaming down my face... B-but it's okay... You have your own reasons for quitting, and I understand... <Sob>
        WELCOME_BACK_LET_S_CHECK_YOUR_TIME_SHALL                              = 10989,  -- Welcome back! Let's check your time, shall we? You cleared the course in # minute[/s] # second[/s].
        OH_MY_GODDESS_YOU_VE_SET_A_NEW                                        = 10990,  -- Oh my Goddess! You've set a new record for this area! Hooray! Somebody, break out the fireworks!
        YOU_VE_SUCCESSFULLY_QUALIFIED_YAY_HERE_S_A                            = 10991,  -- You've successfully qualified! Yay! Here's a little something to commemorate this marvelous achievement.
        YOU_OBTAIN_3                                                          = 10992,  -- You obtain %!
        AH_JUST_THE_KNOWLEDGE_THAT_THERE_RE_CAPABLE                           = 10993,  -- Ah, just the knowledge that there're capable adventurers like you around helps me sleep better at night. The children...they're in good hands... <Sob>
        YOU_DID_JUST_FINE_BUT_DON_T_BE                                        = 10994,  -- You did just fine, but don't be resting on those laurels, you hear? As we smilebringers say, there's always a bigger, brighter smile to be had!
        OH_NO_I_M_AFRAID_YOUR_TIME_FALLS                                      = 10995,  -- Oh no! I'm afraid your time falls short of qualification! As much as I want to give you a passing grade, headquarters wouldn't let me hear the end of it.
        OH_NO_PLEASE_DON_T_BE_MAD_BUT                                         = 10996,  -- Oh no! Please don't be mad, but...I forgot to record your time. I hope you'll find it in your heart to forgive this scatterbrain of a smile sergeant...
        IT_MIGHT_SURPRISE_YOU_TO_LEARN_THIS_BUT                               = 10997,  -- It might surprise you to learn this, but even the toughest--grrrrrr!--and roughest of us smilebringers need rest and relaxation. Oh, wipe that grin off your face! I knew you wouldn't believe me!
        AAANYWAY_WHAT_I_MEANT_TO_SAY_IS_WORK                                  = 10998,  -- Aaanyway! What I meant to say is, work hard, play hard is our motto, and it applies to boot camp participants, too. After you complete a run with a qualifying time--yay!--you're required to rest up until the next day (Vana'diel time).
        AWWW_SEEING_THE_WAY_YOU_RE_SIMPLY_BURSTING                            = 10999,  -- Awww, seeing the way you're simply bursting with enthusiasm makes me want to cry tears of joy. But you have to be cruel to be kind. No more training until tomorrow, young man/lady]! No siree!
