        LET_ME_TAKEY_WAKE_A_STAB_YOU_RE                                       = 11040,  -- Let me takey-wake a stab. You're %, right?
        BOY_AM_I_PLEASED_TO_MEET_YOU_I                                        = 11041,  -- Boy, am I pleased to meet you! I'm Kocchi-Arocchi, and I am out of this world...literally!
        I_SEE_YOU_VE_BROUGHTARU_YOUR_WITH_YOU                                 = 11042,  -- I see you've broughtaru your % with you.
        THE_CAVERNOUS_WAVERNOUS_MAW_HERE_S_CONNECTED_TO                       = 11043,  -- The cavernous-wavernous maw here's connected to Abyssea's take on the Tahrongi Canyon...and it's not proving to be a popular interpretation, I might add.
        CALL_ME_LOWBROW_BUT_I_MUCH_PREFER_THE                                 = 11044,  -- Call me lowbrow, but I much prefer the canyon you've got here. But enough aboutaru myself. I know that you've a mind to see with your own eyes the horrors that lie yonder.
        I_WON_T_STOP_YOU_FROM_MAKING_THE                                      = 11045,  -- I won't stop you from making the journey-wourney. But I am obliged to send you off with a warning: Your destination is fraughtaru with danger. Woooooo`!
        OKAY_NOW_THAT_DUE_WARNING_HAS_BEEN_GIVEN                              = 11046,  -- Okay, now that due warning has been given, I'm going to make an earnest plea for help: Help!
        AHEM_TO_ELABORATE_A_GREATARU_CATACLYSM_HAS_BEFALLEN                   = 11047,  -- Ahem! To elaborate, a greataru cataclysm has befallen Abyssea. The blessing of the moon and the stars no longer reachy-weach us, and the boundary between worlds grows more unstable by the day.
        THE_SITUATION_HAS_DETERIORATED_TO_THE_POINTARU_WHERE                  = 11048,  -- The situation has deteriorated to the pointaru where nothing surprises me anymore. If a dhalmel pie were to appear out of thin air, for instance, I'd be full, but hardly surprised. But I digress-wigress...
        WHERE_WAS_I_AGAIN_OH_RIGHT_WHAT_I                                     = 11049,  -- Where was I again? Oh, right. What I was about to say was, we're being plagued by a giantaru worm. A giantaru worm, I said!
        WHAT_S_THE_BIG_DEAL_MAN_IT_S                                          = 11050,  -- What's the big deal, man? It's only a squishy-wishy worm, you say? To that I retortaru, these worms should've been extinct since the Great War! What's more, this one's suspected of destabilizing the said boundary between worlds!
        VANQUISHING_THIS_PESTI_WESTILENCE_HAS_BECOME_THE_TOP                  = 11051,  -- Vanquishing this pesti-westilence has become the top priority of us survivors. And by association, it's now your priority also!
        NO_ONE_KNOWS_WHETHER_ELIMINATARUING_THE_CREATURE_WOULD                = 11052,  -- No one knows whether eliminataruing the creature would do any good, but what else are we to do?
        OH_BEFORE_I_FORGETARU_THERE_S_SOMETHING_I                             = 11053,  -- Oh, before I forgetaru, there's something I want you to have.
        IT_S_CALLED_CRUOR_DON_T_YOU_JUST                                      = 11054,  -- It's called cruor. Don't you just love the way its deep, red hue is reminiscent of freshly drawn blood?
        IT_S_THE_CURRENCY_IN_CIRCU_WIRCULATION_IN                             = 11055,  -- It's the currency in circu-wirculation in Abyssea. As I can no longer return home, I've no more use for it. Consider it a send-off giftaru for my hero/heroine] who's about to head into grave danger!
        REMEMBER_YOU_MUSTARU_FULFILL_MY_DESTINY_WOOOOOO                       = 11056,  -- Remember, %! You mustaru...fulfill...my destiny! Woooooo`!
        AH_I_WAS_WONDERING_WHEN_YOU_D_COME                                    = 11057,  -- Ah, %! I was wondering when you'd come backy-wack.
        I_KNEW_YOU_WERE_HIGH_CALIBER_WHAT_WITH                                = 11058,  -- I knew you were high caliber--what with your big, bulging muscles and all--but that you would really-weally finish off that giant worm! Amazing! My only regretaru, though, is not having been there to land the killing blow... <Sigh>...
        BUT_THAT_S_BESIDE_THE_POINT_THE_IMPORTANT                             = 11059,  -- But that's beside the point. The important thing is a glimmer-wimmer of hope has been restored to the resistance! From the bottomless chasm of my heart, thank you!
        I_WANTARU_YOU_TO_HAVE_THIS_IT_S                                       = 11060,  -- I wantaru you to have this. It's just this little guy's small way of showing his appreciation.
        IT_S_AND_IT_WORKS_LIKE_A_CHARM                                        = 11061,  -- It's %, and it works like a charm in the hands of a person-werson of your world. No doubtaru it'll come in handy.
        REMEMBER_WEMBER_WHAT_I_SAID_EARLIER_NO_NOT                            = 11062,  -- Remember-wember what I said earlier, %? No, not the part about fulfilling my destiny, but the destabilizing boundary between worlds.
        THIS_WARINESS_INSIDE_ME_DEFIES_WORDS_BUT_I                            = 11063,  -- This wariness inside me defies words, but I have a terrible-werrible foreboding. Laugh at me all you want for a fretting fool, but I intend to stay on my toes...and I suggestaru you do the same.
